    <title>Blogging API</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Blogging API </h2>
    <h3>API Endpoints:</h3>
    <h4>For user :</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>/api/signin - To authenticate the user</li>
        <li>/api/signup - To store the user credentials</li>
    </ul>     
    <hr />
    <h4>For blogs:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>/api/blog             -  Fetch all blog posts</li>
        <li>/api/add/blog         -  Add a new blog along with username</li>
        <li>/api/edit/blog/:id    -  Modify the blog by ID</li>
        <li>/api/remove/blog/:id  -  Remove the blog by ID</li>
    </ul>

</body>
</html>